Welcome to Fy_Shotty_Prison!!

There isn't much to say about this map.  It's been a long time since I've released any work, and this is nothing spectacular, just a good ole' shotgun slugfest!

Any problems/bugs/suggestions direct to:

Email: Phantomoper3@comcast.net
AIM: iRenovatio

(Note: I recommend 16 players, but there are 32 spawn points in all.)
